# Private residue term list — copy to scripts/residue-terms.local (gitignored).
# One case-insensitive extended-regex pattern per line. check-repo.sh scans the
# repo for these and fails if any match — without the terms themselves ever
# being committed. Typical entries: employer names, target companies, personal
# identifiers, internal product names, sibling-repo names.
#
# example-employer-name
# example-target-company
# example-internal-product
